# Hook Performance Ledger

Append-only. Every published post → 7-day score.

**Schema (one row per post per scoring event):**
```
| date_published | date_scored | post_id | preview | format | hook_pattern | reactions | comments | meaningful_comments | reposts | saves | impressions | score | quartile | notes |
```
- `format` — which kk-post format was used (e.g. `6. Share a Helluva Story`)
- `hook_pattern` — `confession` | `reframe` | `specific-number` | `contradiction` | `reader-question` | `inversion` | other
- `meaningful_comments` — comments ≥15 words (amplification signal)
- `saves` — strongest signal (weight heaviest)
- `score` — `reactions + comments×2 + meaningful_comments×3 + reposts×4 + saves×5`
- `quartile` — blank on append; filled by `score-posts`

**Quartiles activate at ≥12 rows.** Below that, no bias — use judgment.

| date_published | date_scored | post_id | preview | format | hook_pattern | reactions | comments | meaningful_comments | reposts | saves | impressions | score | quartile | notes |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|

